{
  "id": "5ff9658794d6ae001dead6dc",
  "title": "非言語コミュニケーション",
  "created": 1610179978,
  "updated": 1721434770,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5ff9658794d6ae001dead6dc",
      "text": "非言語コミュニケーション",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1610179978,
      "updated": 1612874015
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff965ac79d3a90000f9ad70",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/c2b5ee8c6335e94911b6e40158ff6222]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1610180003,
      "updated": 1721433071
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff9659379d3a90000f9ad6e",
      "text": "https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/非言語コミュニケーション より",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1610179978,
      "updated": 1610180012
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff9659379d3a90000f9ad6f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1610179978,
      "updated": 1610179978
    },
    {
      "id": "658264741280f00000bc4f81",
      "text": "情報伝達の65%以上が[非言語情報] by [レイ・バードホイッスル] [takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044213,
      "updated": 1703044235
    },
    {
      "id": "658264971280f00000bc4f84",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044247,
      "updated": 1703044247
    },
    {
      "id": "658264771280f00000bc4f82",
      "text": "[非言語行動]の分類",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044216,
      "updated": 1703044249
    },
    {
      "id": "658264cf1280f00000bc4fad",
      "text": " from [『人間関係における非言語情報伝達』]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044304,
      "updated": 1703044305
    },
    {
      "id": "6582648d1280f00000bc4f83",
      "text": " 1. 体の動き、動作",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044237,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f85",
      "text": "  [表象]([Emblem])",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044337
    },
    {
      "id": "658264f01280f00000bc4faf",
      "text": "   [ジェスチャー]、社会的で共有範囲が広い",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044337,
      "updated": 1703044337
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f88",
      "text": "   例：ドイツの裁判",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044332
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f89",
      "text": "   　頭に指を当てるジェスチャーは、相手を馬鹿だという表現だと裁判で認定された",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f8a",
      "text": "  　意味範囲の広いジェスチャーもある。これは言語も同じ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f8b",
      "text": "  　　あえて[概念 (人の名前)]に狭めないほうがいい場合もある",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f8c",
      "text": "  [イラストレーター]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044342
    },
    {
      "id": "658264f61280f00000bc4fb0",
      "text": "   [抑揚]、[強調]など",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044342,
      "updated": 1703044344
    },
    {
      "id": "658264f81280f00000bc4fb1",
      "text": "   個人的で[共有範囲]が狭く、周囲の人間から学習する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044344,
      "updated": 1703044344
    },
    {
      "id": "658264fc1280f00000bc4fb2",
      "text": "    人によって[怒っているような声]のイントネーションが違うとか？[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044348,
      "updated": 1703044388
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f8d",
      "text": "  [感情表出]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f8e",
      "text": "  [レギュレーター]―[うなずき]や[目配せ]など、人と人との会話の合図",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f8f",
      "text": "   [顔文字]・[絵文字]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f91",
      "text": "   アフリカ系アメリカ人の多いスラムで、韓国人がスーパーを開いた",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f92",
      "text": "   　店員が[人と目を合わせる]なかったので不快に思われ、こじれた",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f93",
      "text": "  　[目線]をあわせる文化でも、ずっと合わせるわけではない？",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f94",
      "text": "  　儒教文化だとあまり目をあわせなさがち？",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f95",
      "text": "  　[うなずき]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f96",
      "text": "  　　[人の話を最後まで聞いてからうなずく]と学んだ人もいる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f97",
      "text": "  　　自分はこまめにうなずくほうだが、別の考えもあるのだな[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f98",
      "text": "  　　逆にこまめにうなずくと、適当に聞いていると思われる場合もある",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f99",
      "text": "  　　[人の話を最後まで聞く]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f9a",
      "text": "  [アダプター]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044396
    },
    {
      "id": "6582652c1280f00000bc4fb3",
      "text": "   いわゆる「[空気を読む]」",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044396,
      "updated": 1703044398
    },
    {
      "id": "6582652e1280f00000bc4fb4",
      "text": "   様々な[兆候]から相手の内面を推測する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044398,
      "updated": 1703044398
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f9b",
      "text": " 2. [身体特徴]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044468
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f9d",
      "text": " 3. [接触行動]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044463
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f9e",
      "text": "  タイだと頭は大事なところだから容易に触るなと言われる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4f9f",
      "text": "   [葬送のフリーレン]タイで展開できないじゃん[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "65828f5a774b1700005d4dfa",
      "text": "    タイが舞台ではないからいいのではw[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1703055195,
      "updated": 1703055216
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4fa0",
      "text": " 4. [準言語]([話し方])",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044431
    },
    {
      "id": "658265691280f00000bc4fbd",
      "text": " 　意図的ではない情報提供",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044457,
      "updated": 1703044457
    },
    {
      "id": "6582654d1280f00000bc4fb5",
      "text": "  声の質",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044429,
      "updated": 1703044433
    },
    {
      "id": "658265511280f00000bc4fb6",
      "text": "  声の性格",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044433,
      "updated": 1703044441
    },
    {
      "id": "65828ec1774b170000cb7ffb",
      "text": "   声の質と声の性格はそれぞれ何を指すんだろ[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1703055042,
      "updated": 1703055063
    },
    {
      "id": "658265591280f00000bc4fb7",
      "text": "  [間投詞",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044441,
      "updated": 1703044447
    },
    {
      "id": "6582655b1280f00000bc4fb8",
      "text": "  [沈黙]や[反応時間]、[言い間違い]に対する訂正",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044443,
      "updated": 1703044443
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4fa3",
      "text": " 5. [近接学]([Proxemics])",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044487
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4fa4",
      "text": "  [距離感]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4fa5",
      "text": "  [フリーレン.icon]「[他者との距離感]って何？」",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044500
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4fa6",
      "text": "  人によって[パーソナルスペース]がことなる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4fa7",
      "text": "  近すぎて不快な例：[満員電車]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4faa",
      "text": " 6. 人口品",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044514
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4fab",
      "text": "  かつらを[お笑い]と捉える文化",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044289
    },
    {
      "id": "658265ac1280f00000bc4fc1",
      "text": "  洋服も非言語情報になりうる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044524,
      "updated": 1703044539
    },
    {
      "id": "658264c11280f00000bc4fac",
      "text": " 7. [環境因子]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044289,
      "updated": 1703044517
    },
    {
      "id": "658265a41280f00000bc4fbf",
      "text": "  建築、室内装飾、照明、におい、色、温度、騒音、音楽、物の配置",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044517,
      "updated": 1703044517
    },
    {
      "id": "658265a51280f00000bc4fc0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044517,
      "updated": 1703044517
    },
    {
      "id": "658265c21280f00000bc4fc2",
      "text": "講義スライドの文章が半分くらい混ざってるけど、ここに書いて大丈夫だったかな……[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1703044547,
      "updated": 1703044566
    },
    {
      "id": "658265c71280f00000bc4fc3",
      "text": "　勉強になりまうす[sume.icon][kana.icon]",
      "userId": "5e9487d750011b001eb536eb",
      "created": 1703044551,
      "updated": 1721434770
    },
    {
      "id": "6582a1e15b98c20000abb92a",
      "text": "[言語コミュニケーション]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1703059938,
      "updated": 1703059946
    },
    {
      "id": "6582a1e55b98c20000abb92c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1703059942,
      "updated": 1703059942
    }
  ]
}